{"tid":1218671,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【文宣部入】 香 港 人 沒 有 時 間 傷 心 ！！！！！！","createTime":"2019-06-13T16:27:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-13T16:38:30.000Z","uid":162866,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"05337e27f89ded97175ff06b1e5430d4eb8e6891","tid":1218671,"uid":162866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T16:27:41.000Z","msg":"經過今次暴力清場好多本來無出聲既人都醒覺了<br />\n<br />\n而今個星期日就係呢班silent majority有機會表達佢地意見既舞台<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但因為時間不足暫時16號民陣個遊行都係好少人知<br />\n<br />\n希望大家化身為文宣部幫手宣傳16號<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果一個禮拜內有2個100萬人大遊行輿論將會係壓倒性<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c6afe130818271764b400ea2621b089f03c38b9","tid":1218671,"uid":162866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T16:29:24.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"f78bdd930178c5a442d53c0cba62d882005c7683","tid":1218671,"uid":5809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T16:30:16.000Z","msg":"幫推<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">咁多位香港人,大家認為星期日上街係為左咩!?<br />\n<br />\n為左抗惡法?無錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n為咗迫林鄭下台?無錯</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>但最重要既係保護香港人!!!!!!!!!!</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n暫時最少已經有11個香港人為咗我地被捕<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n當中包括為咗我地而食棍!!!中椒!!!同埋中槍既香港人!!!!!!<br />\n星期日上街我地一定要為佢地發聲!!!唔可以忘記佢地!!!!!<br />\n<br />\n大家集中目標:<br />\n1.撤回送中惡法<br />\n2.林鄭及相關官員必須問責下台<br />\n3.釋放所有被捕人士及保證不會檢控任何示威者<br />\n4.起訴涉嫌謀殺之警員及其上司<br />\n5.成立具效力之警方濫用暴力調查組織<br />\n6.釋放所有在囚政治人士,包括黃之鋒及梁天琦<br />\n<br />\n<strong>香港人,記得一個都不能少!!!!!!<br />\n<br />\n唔可以放棄任何一個自己人!!!!!!</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"622251f0f0590a833c6614c05d7dd2667a670b3f","tid":1218671,"uid":162866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T16:30:59.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"054cf548f6f56d10ad314073bc7c4bcab8b0fdd1","tid":1218671,"uid":139677,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T16:32:16.000Z","msg":"用616<span style=\"color: green;\">和平</span>遊行宣傳好似好啲<br />\n要理解經過呢幾日之後大眾嘅憂慮"},{"pid":"49be9f553fcaea84deee0ac781f7470bea53f066","tid":1218671,"uid":162866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T16:38:30.000Z","msg":"66"}]}